The German language pack contains several new translations which contain invalid characters instead of Umlauts, for example in editor tooltips. These characters are displayed as a black square with a question mark. Please see the attached screenshot for an example.

{noformat}
tinymce.atlassian.insert_menu.hr_desc=Horizontale Trennlinie einf\uFFFDgen (----) 
{noformat}

It should be:

{noformat}
tinymce.atlassian.insert_menu.hr_desc=Horizontale Trennlinie einf\u00FCgen (----) 
{noformat}

All message keys can be found by searching for "\uFFFD" in the properties files.

I corrected all occurences at translations.atlassian.com.

